    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>I'm working on a rather rare muscle disease</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172709Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T162543Z">
        <seg>Je travaille sur une maladie musculaire plutôt rare :</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>If on the other hand I'm a clinician I believe that</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152414Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152414Z">
        <seg>mais en tant que clinicien, je reste persuadé que</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>In fact this is the first phase-3 trial</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T164600Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T164600Z">
        <seg>En réalité, il s'agit du premier essai clinique de phase 3</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>In the past, it was called also</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172751Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T162857Z">
        <seg>anciennement appelée</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>International Center for Life in Newcastle.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T142103Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T142103Z">
        <seg> du centre international de Newcastle.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>It's an adult-onset myopathy</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172846Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T163516Z">
        <seg>Il s'agit d'une myopathie se déclarant à l'âge adulte,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>John Wharton muscle team at the</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T142031Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T142031Z">
        <seg>l'équipe de pathologie musculaire John Walton</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>Most of the patients are Duchenne or Becker</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T141048Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T140924Z">
        <seg>La plupart des patients sont de type Duchenne ou Becker,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>Organisations like the AFM will play a big role</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172046Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T151105Z">
        <seg>Des entités comme l'AFM jouent un rôle déterminant</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So I think it's more an effect of saying</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152941Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152941Z">
        <seg>Pour résumer, le paradoxe est que</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So I'm a clinical cardiologist and I run</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T155150Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T120146Z">
        <seg>En tant que cardiologue clinicien, je mène</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So essentially, if I'm a scientist I would say that the study is negative.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152327Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152327Z">
        <seg>Donc, en tant que scientifique, je dirais que l’étude est négative,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So for the collagen VI genes, it is interesting that</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T165808Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T131950Z">
        <seg>Pour les gènes du collagène VI, il est intéressant de noter</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So that is the goal, in our laboratories,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T150339Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T150339Z">
        <seg>L'objectif principal de nos laboratoires</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So we're hoping to follow the patients for longer.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152000Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152000Z">
        <seg>Il nous faut donc suivre ces patients plus longtemps.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So, eighty five boys were recruited</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T145257Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T145138Z">
        <seg>Notre étude porte sur 85 garçons,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>So, the research funding is critical,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T155002Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T154802Z">
        <seg>Le financement de la recherche est donc essentiel.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>Somewhat disappointingly, the results do not show</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T151312Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T151102Z">
        <seg>Nous n'avons hélas pas encore constaté d'amélioration</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>That is particularly relevant for a new and common mutation,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T171039Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T141358Z">
        <seg>Une approche particulièrement pertinente pour la nouvelle mutation,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>The AFM I think is essential to maintaining</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T153644Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T153443Z">
        <seg>Je pense que l’AFM est essentiel au maintien</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>The AFM of course is pivotal in providing</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T153122Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T153122Z">
        <seg>L’AFM joue un rôle essentiel en assurant le financement</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>The difficulty in that study was that</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T182418Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T182418Z">
        <seg>La difficulté de cette étude résidait dans le fait</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>The main focus of my research</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T142121Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T142121Z">
        <seg>Le principal objectif de mes recherches</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>There are 3 collagen VI genes and mutations</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T165558Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T131300Z">
        <seg>Il existe 3 gènes du collagène VI, et des mutations </seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>There are beginning to be some changes</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152110Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152110Z">
        <seg>Il commence à y avoir des changements</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>This is a highly individualised therapy,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T171543Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T143429Z">
        <seg>Cette approche hautement individualisée,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>This is caused by mutations in the collagen VI genes.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T165526Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T131035Z">
        <seg>liée à des mutations sur les gènes du collagène VI.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>This is really a prime example of precision medicine,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T171702Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T145752Z">
        <seg>Vraiment un excellent exemple de la médecine de précision,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>Ullrich congenital muscular dystrophy.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T165516Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T130813Z">
        <seg>de dystrophie musculaire congénitale d'Ullrich,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>Usually the onset is in the early adulthood,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T164120Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T164120Z">
        <seg>Elle se déclare généralement au début de l'âge adulte,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are devising fair pieces, trying to detoxify</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T170702Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T134159Z">
        <seg>Notre approche consiste à créer des "morceaux sains"</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are particularly working on a  type called</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T130540Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T130540Z">
        <seg>Nous travaillons en particulier sur un type appelé</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are trying to "knock down" the mutation readout</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T170820Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T140158Z">
        <seg>Nous essayons ainsi d'"enrayer" la lecture de la mutation</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are trying to skip that out using oligo-nuclear type therapies.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T171453Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T142834Z">
        <seg>Nous essayons d'éviter cela avec des thérapies de type oligonucléotide.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are trying to understand how the mutations</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T131443Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T131443Z">
        <seg>Nous essayons de comprendre comment les mutations</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We are working on congenital muscular dystrophies,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T165210Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T125533Z">
        <seg>Nous travaillons sur les dystrophies musculaires congénitales.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We recently had a phase-3 trial.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T164424Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T164424Z">
        <seg>Nous avons récemment lancé un essai clinique de phase 3.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>We treated them with a combination of</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T145409Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T145409Z">
        <seg>Nous les avons traités avec une association de</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>[Music]</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T160512Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T120023Z">
        <seg>[Musique]</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>a dedicated cardiology clinic for</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T140204Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T121202Z">
        <seg>une étude clinique spécialisée en cardiologie</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>a mutation that has been hidden from our analysis so far,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T171201Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T141621Z">
        <seg>une mutation qui avait échappé jusqu'à présent à notre analyse,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and I work very closely with</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T141148Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T141148Z">
        <seg>Je travaille en étroite collaboration avec</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and a beta blocker : prepared bisoprolol.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T155546Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T150404Z">
        <seg>et de bêta-bloquant : une préparation de bisoprolol.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and all of the CRISPR cross approaches.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T170946Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T141025Z">
        <seg>nous appuyant sur les approches transversales CRISPR.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and followed for a minimum of three years.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T145346Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T145329Z">
        <seg>et suivis pendant au moins trois ans.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and for patients that are not large in number,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172159Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T151703Z">
        <seg>et pour un petit nombre de patients.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and is allowing translation of research,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T153935Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T153935Z">
        <seg>permettant une conversion plus rapide des recherches</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and it also ensures a balance between</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T153702Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T153403Z">
        <seg>Cet organisme assure également un équilibre entre</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and slowly progressing to affect</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172905Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T163731Z">
        <seg>et qui s'étend ensuite progressivement</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and so that is a project that by necessity</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172228Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T151856Z">
        <seg>Un tel projet nécessite, inévitablement,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and that causes a pseudo-exon and a toxic pseudo-exon,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T141702Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T141702Z">
        <seg>et qui provoque un pseudo-exon et un pseudo-exon toxique,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and the AFM will play a big role in</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172431Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T152622Z">
        <seg>En cela, l'AFM joue un rôle essentiel </seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and the disease progresses slowly</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172928Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T164137Z">
        <seg>puis la maladie progresse lentement</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and the relevance of basic science and molecular biology</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T154150Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T154150Z">
        <seg>et découvertes fondamentales, en particulier en biologie moléculaire,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and the variation in the age of onset of muscle weakness</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T151711Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T151553Z">
        <seg>l'évolution d'une faiblesse musculaire venant d'apparaitre</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>and there was a placebo comparator group.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T150727Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T150727Z">
        <seg>Un groupe de comparaison a reçu des placebos.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>any group benefit after three years of treatment</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T151243Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T151243Z">
        <seg>dans aucun groupe après trois ans de traitement,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>at the moment we have to conclude,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152154Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152154Z">
        <seg>pour le moment nous devons conclure</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>because we know already that once we detect</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T152644Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T152644Z">
        <seg>car nous savons qu'une fois une faiblesse musculaire</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>beginning in the distal muscles of the legs,</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="joce" changedate="20190328T163620Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T163620Z">
        <seg>commençant dans les muscles distaux des jambes,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>between the ages of five and thirteen</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T145336Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T145240Z">
        <seg>âgés de cinq à treize ans</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>but there's a mixture of other conditions</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T141114Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T141044Z">
        <seg>avec aussi un mélange d'autres tableaux cliniques.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>but we think that's partly explained</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190327T151352Z" creationid="fred" creationdate="20190327T151352Z">
        <seg>mais nous pensons que cela s'explique en partie</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>by patient advocacy</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="FR-FR" changeid="fred" changedate="20190328T172402Z" creationid="joce" creationdate="20190328T152539Z">
        <seg>ou par des associations de patients.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-GB">
        <seg>by the fact that younger patients,</seg>
